Renamed variables, removed errant letters. Greatly reworked musician view logic. Data fetches now queue async callback function for one setState call. Removed derived data from state. Work on improving view, mobile still needs sorted. Lots of refactoring with Nathan (terakilobyte)
Streamlined some code, removed style from musician table
Streamlined some code, removed style from musician table
Rewrite facility info retrieval
Comment out console.log statements and remove unused code blocks
Return correct facility contact info for each event
Remove h5 for bootswatch simplex

Added javascript DOM node positioning and style setting for StatusCard to show event details. Added renderOffset(offset) function to EventContainer to store offset for new status card update in state. Sending EventCard a renderOffset prop. EventContainer passes offset prop to StatusCard so it can render in proper position. Added componentDidUpdate code and placeDiv method for rendering the StatusCard in the proper position.

Added call to this.placeDiv in componentDidMount to account for first click event top positioning; added a slideTransition class to the StatusCard render code parent div; added the .slideTransition in main.less to provide for smooth animation on top property
All admin screens now share same panel style.

Bootstrap column spacing changed from sm style to xs style.
Admin/Facility now works and looks like Admin/Events.
